				<h1><a href="http://www.cruxnow.com/church/2015/02/19/san-francisco-catholic-school-morality-clause-dispute/" rel="next">The dispute over morality clauses is roiling San Francisco's Catholics</a></h1>
		    </header>
		    <p class="abstract">The archdiocese is trying to make its Catholic schools more Catholic, but city and state officials are pushing back, saying any effort to discriminate against employees will be met with legal action. <a href="http://www.cruxnow.com/church/2015/02/19/san-francisco-catholic-school-morality-clause-dispute/#begin_comments" class="digest_comments comment_counter_container" rel="next"><span class="comment_counter" data-post-id="115132"></span> <i> &#xf075; </i></a></p>
            <div class="abstract_byline_n">By <a href="http://www.cruxnow.com/author/nyt"><span class="byline_name_n">Jill Tucker</span></a><br class="byline_splitter" /><a href="http://www.cruxnow.com/author/nyt"><span class="byline_affiliation_n">San Francisco Chronicle</span></a></div>
