	<article id="post-114931" class="teaser special_teaser" role="article">
		<header>
			<p class="small_label_special"><a href="http://www.cruxnow.com/tag/lent/" rel="next">Lent</a></p>
		</header>
		<a href="http://www.cruxnow.com/faith/2015/02/18/confessions-of-a-lenten-slacker/" rel="next">
			<figure class="teaser_image_special"><picture class="ie8-hidden"><!--[if IE 9]><video style="display: none;"><![endif]--><source srcset="http://static.cruxnow.com/uploads/2015/02/Fasting-C-502x287.jpg" media="(min-width: 950px)" /><source srcset="http://static.cruxnow.com/uploads/2015/02/Fasting-C-717x450.jpg" media="(min-width: 900px)" /><source srcset="http://static.cruxnow.com/uploads/2015/02/Fasting-C-502x287.jpg" media="(min-width: 750px)" /><source srcset="http://static.cruxnow.com/uploads/2015/02/Fasting-C-717x450.jpg" media="(min-width: 600px)" /><source srcset="http://static.cruxnow.com/uploads/2015/02/Fasting-C-502x287.jpg" media="(min-width: 451px)" /><source srcset="http://static.cruxnow.com/uploads/2015/02/Fasting-C-412x235.jpg" media="(min-width: 321px)" /><source srcset="http://static.cruxnow.com/uploads/2015/02/Fasting-C-283x162.jpg" media="(min-width: 1px)" /><!--[if IE 9]></video><![endif]--><img scrset="http://static.cruxnow.com/uploads/2015/02/Fasting-C-502x287.jpg" alt="Fasting-C" class="ie8-hidden" /></picture><!--[if lte IE 8]><img src="http://static.cruxnow.com/uploads/2015/02/Fasting-C-502x287.jpg" alt="Fasting-C" width="502" height="287" /><![endif]--></figure>
			<h3><span class="hover">Confessions of a Lenten slacker</span></h3>
		</a>
		<section class="teaser_text_container">
			<p class="abstract">
				Given the relaxation of Catholic discipline over the centuries, maybe now’s the time to ask some hard questions: Should Catholics go back to more rigorous fasting and abstinence? Should Lent really count for something? <a href="http://www.cruxnow.com/faith/2015/02/18/confessions-of-a-lenten-slacker/#begin_comments" class="digest_comments comment_counter_container" rel="next"><span class="comment_counter" data-post-id="114931"></span> <i> &#xf075; </i></a>
			</p>
            <footer class="byline_container"><div class="abstract_byline_special_mug clearfix"><a href="http://www.cruxnow.com/author/mathew-schmalz" class="special_treatment">By <span class="byline_name_n">Mathew N. Schmalz</span></a><br class="byline_splitter" /><a href="http://www.cruxnow.com/author/mathew-schmalz"><span class="byline_affiliation_n">Crux contributor</span></a></div></footer>
			
			
			<aside class="story_refer"><a href="http://www.cruxnow.com/life/2015/02/18/your-ashtag-selfies/" rel="next"><span>related </span>Your #ashtag selfies</a></aside>
		</section>
	</article>


			</section>
