				I will not be sneaking about today, hiding my smudged forehead under cover of darkness. Should anyone ask, I’ll tell them: In the age of Francis, the good shepherds have been liberated. <a href="http://www.cruxnow.com/faith/2015/02/18/defending-my-forehead-and-my-faith/#begin_comments" class="digest_comments comment_counter_container" rel="next"><span class="comment_counter" data-post-id="114877"></span> <i> &#xf075; </i></a>
