				If God brought all this snow, he also made it very hard to get to church. But the liturgy goes on, and that can mean a priest snowshoes to work or delivers a sermon via Facebook. <a href="http://www.cruxnow.com/faith/2015/02/18/in-the-face-of-unrelenting-snow-new-england-churches-soldier-on/#begin_comments" class="digest_comments comment_counter_container" rel="next"><span class="comment_counter" data-post-id="115082"></span> <i> &#xf075; </i></a>
