	<article class="teaser special_teaser">
		<header>
			<p class="small_label_special"><a href="http://www.cruxnow.com/tag/commentary/" rel="next">Commentary</a></p>
			<h2 class="headline_special"><a href="http://www.cruxnow.com/faith/2015/02/17/50-years-of-christian-jewish-revolution-what-we-can-all-learn-commentary/" rel="next">50 years of Catholic-Jewish revolution: What we all can learn</a></h2>
		</header>
		<section class="teaser_text_container teaser_text_container_special">
							<a href="http://www.cruxnow.com/faith/2015/02/17/50-years-of-christian-jewish-revolution-what-we-can-all-learn-commentary/" rel="next"><figure class="teaser_image_small"><picture class="ie8-hidden"><!--[if IE 9]><video style="display: none;"><![endif]--><source srcset="http://static.cruxnow.com/uploads/2015/02/Pope-John-XXIII-283x162.jpg" media="(min-width: 950px)" /><source srcset="http://static.cruxnow.com/uploads/2015/02/Pope-John-XXIII-322x184.jpg" media="(min-width: 451px)" /><source srcset="http://static.cruxnow.com/uploads/2015/02/Pope-John-XXIII-412x235.jpg" media="(min-width: 321px)" /><source srcset="http://static.cruxnow.com/uploads/2015/02/Pope-John-XXIII-283x162.jpg" media="(min-width: 1px)" /><!--[if IE 9]></video><![endif]--><img scrset="http://static.cruxnow.com/uploads/2015/02/Pope-John-XXIII-322x184.jpg" alt="Pope John XXIII addressed the assembled bishops at the opening of the Second Vatican Council." class="ie8-hidden" /></picture><!--[if lte IE 8]><img src="http://static.cruxnow.com/uploads/2015/02/Pope-John-XXIII-322x184.jpg" alt="Pope John XXIII addressed the assembled bishops at the opening of the Second Vatican Council." width="322" height="184" /><![endif]--></figure></a>
						<p class="abstract">
				If one religion (Catholicism) can go from seeing another (Judaism) as contemptible and condemnable, to one that is respected and beloved, it can surely serve as a model for humanity at large. <a href="http://www.cruxnow.com/faith/2015/02/17/50-years-of-christian-jewish-revolution-what-we-can-all-learn-commentary/#begin_comments" class="digest_comments comment_counter_container" rel="next"><span class="comment_counter" data-post-id="114033"></span> <i> &#xf075; </i></a>
			</p>
